Package com.tome25.utils.logging

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LoggingPrintStream
    A PrintStream that writes everything to a Logger.
    LogTracer
    A utility class to improve logging.
    Used to trace the system outputs, and to get custom Loggers logging to the system output.
    MultiPrintStream
    A standard PrintStream except it can write to multiple OutputStreams.
    OutputHandler
    A StreamHandler that can have a custom log Level from the start.
    SplittingHandler
    A Handler that splits LogRecords into System.out and System.err based on their log Level.
    TracingFormatter
    A custom Formatter for the tracing log style.
    TracingMultiPrintStream
    A Tracing PrintStream that can print to multiple OutputStreams.
